@page
@model DocumentationModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Documentation";
}
<h3>@ViewData["Title"]</h3>

<br />

<body>
    <section id="project-overview">
        <h4>Project Overview:</h4>
        <h4>Name: Srija Pal</h4>
        <p>
            <strong>Project Description:</strong> This project is a basic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) application integrated with a chatbot and an image slider. The CRUD application allows users to perform basic operations on a database, while the chatbot provides predefined responses to user queries. Additionally, an image slider feature enhances the visual appeal of the application.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section id="detailed-components">
        <h2>Detailed Components:</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h3>CRUD Application:</h3>
                <p>The CRUD application allows users to perform the following operations on a database:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create: Add new records to the database.</li>
                    <li>Read: Retrieve and view existing records from the database.</li>
                    <li>Update: Modify existing records in the database.</li>
                    <li>Delete: Remove records from the database.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Chatbot:</h3>
                <p>The chatbot feature provides predefined responses to user queries. It enhances user interaction within the application by providing automated responses based on predefined rules or algorithms.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Image Slider:</h3>
                <p>The image slider feature displays a series of images in a slideshow format, adding visual appeal and interactivity to the application's user interface.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>
    <section id="technologies">
        <h2>Technologies:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Database Management:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>SQL Express: Utilized for managing the application's database, including storing and retrieving data for CRUD operations.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="learning-experience">
        <h2>Learning Experience:</h2>
        <p>During the development of this project, I gained valuable experience in the following areas:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Database management using SQL Express.</li>
            <li>Integrating chatbot functionality into web applications.</li>
            <li>Implementing image sliders for enhanced user experience.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>This project has provided a valuable learning experience in developing a basic CRUD application with additional features such as a chatbot and an image slider. The utilization of SQL Express for database management has enhanced my understanding of relational databases and SQL queries. Moving forward, I look forward to applying these skills in future projects and endeavors.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
